Package org.cruk.genologics.api.jaxb

Classes to aid the JAXB object mapping process.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDateAdapter
    Base for date adapters.
    JaxbMarshallingTool
    Tool to help debugging: a short cut for marshalling an object to a string.
    JaxbUnmarshallingAspect
    Aspect that wraps the unmarshalling of responses from the Genologics API.
    KnownNamespacePrefixMatcher
    Implementation of the internal Sun JAXB NamespacePrefixMapper to make sure the XML documents created from JAXB have user friendly name spaces in their headers.
    LongTimestampAdapter
    Adapter for those dates that are exchanged with the API in the long timestamp format.
    ShortDateAdapter
    Adapter for those dates that are exchanged with the API in the short date only format.
    URIAdapter
    Convert to and from URI objects, correctly encoding the query string.
